title: GameMaker-Studio Master Collection Auto-Update Experimental V2
description:
Ok here comes V2, this one has a lot of hanges and should fix most if not all bugs people have been recieving with V1.

As of now this will update you to 1.1.1089, but as this is a auto updater it will keep you up to date with the latest version of GMS.

I have included a cleanup tool with this release, i HIGHLY recomend that you run it. Make sure you uninstall any previous release that you may have, as well as any YoYo releases as to prevent problems.

If you do find a problem and are unable to launch, go to the directory where you installed GameMaker and zip up the logs folder and upload it somewhere so i can help as best as i can. By default the log folder will be in "C:Users{UserName}AppDataRoamingGameMaker-Studiologs"

Enjoy ;D
